<div class="main-body">
  <div class="page-wrapper">
    <div class="page-header">
      <div class="page-header-title">
        <h4>기사선택</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="page-header-breadcrumb">
        <ul class="breadcrumb-title">
          <li class="breadcrumb-item">
            <a href="/">
              <i class="fas fa-home"></i>
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="#!">기사선택</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="page-body">
      <div class="row" id="listTable">
        <div class="col-md-12">
          <div class="alert alert-default" style="border-radius:  0; border-width:  2px;  margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          	<ul class="p-l-15 f-12" style="list-style-type: disc; color:  #666;">
              <!-- <li>기사의 썸네일은 넣고자 하는 이미지의 URL 주소를 해당 기사의 박스 칸에 작성하시면 됩니다.</li> -->
              <li>해당 기사의 그룹핑 버튼을 누르면 기사 제목을 기준으로 날짜와 검색어 조건을 적용하여 관련 기사 리스트가 보여집니다.</li>
              <li>대분류, 세부기사 수정 및 선택기사 삭제는 선택기사 리스트 페이지에서 할 수있습니다.</li>
              <li>대표기사에 있는 번호를 다른 기사의 세부기사 칸에 작성해주시면 기사 그룹핑이 됩니다.</li>
          	</ul>
        	</div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-12">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
              <select name="select" class="col-md-1 form-control form-control-default m-b-10 m-r-5 p-r-5 f-left" id="selectKeyword">
                <option>키워드</option>
                <%for(var i=0; i < klist.length; i++) {%>
                  <option value='<%=klist[i].keyword_main%>'><%=klist[i].keyword_main%></option>
                <%}%>
              </select>
              <select class="form-control col-md-1 form-control-default m-r-5 m-b-10 f-left" id="selectNewsType">
                <option value="0">대분류</option>
                <option value="1">쇼박스영화</option>
                <option value="2">경쟁영화</option>
                <option value="3">캐스팅</option>
                <option value="4">쇼박스기업뉴스</option>
                <option value="5">영화일반</option>
                <option value="6">보도국</option>
                <option value="7">박스오피스</option>
              </select>
              <select class="form-control col-md-1 form-control-default m-r-5 m-b-10 f-left" id="selectSite">
                <option value="all">사이트</option>
                <option value="naver">네이버</option>
                <option value="daum">다음</option>
                <option value="out">기타</option>
              </select>
              <select class="form-control col-md-1 form-control-default m-r-5 m-b-10 f-left" id="selectNum">
                <option value="30">30</option>
                <option value="50">50</option>
                <option value="100">100</option>
              </select>
              <!-- <button class="btn btn-primary searchBtn">단독</button> -->
              <!-- <button class="btn btn-primary searchBtn">공식</button> -->
              <div class="col-sm-3 p-l-0 p-t-5 m-b-10 f-left border-checkbox-section checkbox-news">
                <div class="border-checkbox-group border-checkbox-group-default m-r-5">
                  <input class="border-checkbox" type="checkbox" id="searchBtn1" name="search" value="단독">
                  <label class="border-checkbox-label" for="searchBtn1">단독</label>
                </div>
                <div class="border-checkbox-group border-checkbox-group-default m-r-5" >
                  <input class="border-checkbox" type="checkbox" id="searchBtn2" name="search" value="공식">
                  <label class="border-checkbox-label" for="searchBtn2">공식</label>
                </div>
                <div class="border-checkbox-group border-checkbox-group-default m-r-5">
                  <input class="border-checkbox" type="checkbox" id="searchMediaBtn" name="video" value="ture">
                  <label class="border-checkbox-label" for="searchMediaBtn">영상</label>
                </div>
                <div class="border-checkbox-group border-checkbox-group-default m-r-5">
                  <input class="border-checkbox" type="checkbox" id="searchRankBtn" name="rank" value="ture">
                  <label class="border-checkbox-label" for="searchRankBtn">순위</label>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-12 col-md-2 f-right col-sm-9 m-l-10 p-l-0 p-r-0 m-b-10 right-icon-control" style= "min-width: 207px;">
                <input type="text" class="form-control p-t-10 form-control-default search-text" value="<%= search %>" placeholder="제목/내용 검색" id="searchInput">
                <div class="form-icon" id="searchBtn">
                  <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-2 p-r-0 p-l-0 f-right reportrange">
                <div id="reportrange" class="form-control form-control-default">
                  <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar far fa-calendar-alt"></i>
                  <span></span>
                  <i class="f-right fa fa-angle-down" style="font-size: 17px;"></i>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-block table-border-style">
              <div class="preloader3 loader-block">
                <div class="circ1 loader-primary"></div>
                <div class="circ2 loader-primary"></div>
                <div class="circ3 loader-primary"></div>
                <div class="circ4 loader-primary"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="preloader2 loader-block">
              <svg id="loader2" viewBox="0 0 100 100">
                <circle id="circle-loader2" cx="50" cy="50" r="45"></circle>
              </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="table-responsive">
                <table class="table">
                  <thead>
                    <tr>
                      <th width="1%">
                        <div class="border-checkbox-section" style="max-width: 30px;">
                          <div class="border-checkbox-group border-checkbox-group-default">
                            <input class="border-checkbox" type="checkbox" id="checkboxAll">
                            <label class="border-checkbox-label" for="checkboxAll"></label>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </th>
                      <th width="5%">NO</th>
                      <th width="10%" style="min-width: 60px;">작성날짜</th>
                      <th width="10%" style="min-width: 60px;">보고날짜</th>
                      <th width="20%">제목</th>
                      <th width="5%" style="min-width: 100px;">언론사</th>
                      <th width="5%" style="min-width: 80px;">기자</th>
                      <th width="5%">순위</th>
                      <th width="5%" style="min-width: 80px;">키워드</th>
                      <th width="5%" style="min-width: 50px;">분류글</th>
                      <!-- <th width="20%" style="min-width: 120px;">썸네일</th> -->
                      <th width="10%" style="min-width: 140px;">대분류</th>
                      <th width="10%" style="min-width: 100px;">대표기사</th>
                      <th width="10%" style="min-width: 100px;">세부기사</th>
                    </tr>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody>
                    <%
                      if(currentPage > 0){
                        (currentPage - 1) * limit;
                      }
                      for(var i=0; i < list.length; i++) {
                    %>
                    <tr>
                      <input type="hidden" id="idx" value="<%=list[i].media_idx%>" />
                      <td>
                        <div class="border-checkbox-section" style="max-width: 30px;">
                          <div class="border-checkbox-group border-checkbox-group-default">
                            <input type="hidden" name="a" value="<%= list[i].news_idx %>">
                            <input class="border-checkbox news-checkbox" type="checkbox" id="checkbox<%=i%>" <%=(list[i].news_idx != null) ? 'checked' : ''%>>
                            <label class="border-checkbox-label" for="checkbox<%=i%>"></label>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </td>
                      <th><%= listCount - i - offset %></th>
                      <td><div class="date_nobr"><%= list[i].writeDate %></div></td>
                      <td><input type="text" name="datefilter" class="datepicker form-control" value="<%= list[i].reportDate %>"/></td>
                      <td>
                        <a href="<%= list[i].url %>" target="_blank" title="<%= list[i].media_title %>">
                          <div class="title_nobr">
                            <% if (list[i].media_subname != 'out'){%>
                              <img alt="<%=list[i].media_subname%>" src="http://showbox.email/images/newsclipping/<%=list[i].media_subname%>_logo.png" class="site-logo">
                            <% } %>
                            <%= list[i].media_title %>
                          </div>
                        </a>
                        <!-- <i class="far fa-file-video text-muted"></i> -->
                        <i class="fas fa-video text-muted" style="<%=(list[i].v_state != 2) ? 'visibility: hidden' : ''%>"></i>
                        <div class="label-main group" style="margin-right:  0px;display: inline;">
                          <label class="label label-md label-default" style="margin-right:  0px;">그룹핑</label>
                        </div>
                      </td>
                      <!-- <td><div class="media_nobr" title="<%= list[i].media_name %>"><%= list[i].media_name %></div></td> -->
                      <td><input type="text" placeholder="<%=list[i].media_name%>" id="media_name" value="<%=list[i].media_name%>" class="form-control selectText"></td>
                      <td><input type="text" placeholder="<%=list[i].reporter_name%>" id="reporter_name" value="<%=list[i].reporter_name%>" class="form-control selectText"></td>
                      <td>
                        <div class="rank_nobr">
                          <% if(list[i].ME_rank == null){ %>
                            <i class="fas fa-minus"></i>
                          <%}else{%>
                            <%=list[i].ME_rank+'위'%>
                          <%}%>
                        </div>
                      </td>
                      <td><div class="key_nobr" title="<%= list[i].keyword %>"><%= list[i].keyword %></div></td>
                      <td>
                        <div class="nobr" title="<%= list[i].textType %>">
                          <% if(list[i].textType == null){ %>
                            <i class="fas fa-minus"></i>
                          <%}else{%>
                            <%=list[i].textType%>
                          <%}%>
                        </div>
                      </td>
                      <!-- <td>
                        <input type="text" placeholder="이미지주소(URL)" id="thumbnail" class="form-control selectText">
                      </td> -->
                      <td>
                        <!-- <input type="number" min="1" max="8" value="1"  id="newsType" class="form-control"> -->
                        <select class="form-control form-control-default p-l-5 select-news" id="newsType">
                          <option value="0" <%=(list[i].news_type == '0') ? 'selected' : ''%>>-</option>
                          <option value="1" <%=(list[i].news_type == '1') ? 'selected' : (list[i].title_key == '쇼박스영화') ? 'selected' : ''%>>쇼박스영화</option>
                          <option value="2" <%=(list[i].news_type == '2') ? 'selected' : (list[i].title_key == '경쟁영화') ? 'selected' : ''%>>경쟁영화</option>
                          <option value="3" <%=(list[i].news_type == '3') ? 'selected' : (list[i].title_key == '캐스팅') ? 'selected' : ''%>>캐스팅</option>
                          <option value="4" <%=(list[i].news_type == '4') ? 'selected' : (list[i].title_key == '쇼박스기업뉴스' || list[i].title_key == '오리온') ? 'selected' : ''%>>쇼박스기업뉴스</option>
                          <option value="5" <%=(list[i].news_type == '5') ? 'selected' : (list[i].title_key == '영화일반') ? 'selected' : ''%>>영화일반</option>
                          <option value="6" <%=(list[i].news_type == '6') ? 'selected' : (list[i].title_key == '보도국') ? 'selected' : ''%>>보도국</option>
                          <option value="7" <%=(list[i].news_type == '7') ? 'selected' : (list[i].title_key == '박스오피스') ? 'selected' : ''%>>박스오피스</option>
                        </select>
                      </td>
                      <td>
                        <input type="text" placeholder="대표기사" id="news_title" value="<%=list[i].media_idx%>" class="form-control selectText">
                      </td>
                      <td>
                        <input type="text" placeholder="세부기사" id="news_detail" class="form-control selectText">
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <% } %>
                  </tbody>
                  <tfoot>
                    <tr>
                    <%
                    var pageCount = Math.ceil(listCount/limit);
                    if(pageCount > 1) {
                    %>
                      <td colspan="5">
                        <button id="addBtn" class="btn btn-list alert-check p-r-5 p-l-5 m-l-15 m-b-5  f-left m-t-5"><i class="fas fa-angle-down"></i>선택저장</button>
                      </td>
                      <td colspan="8">
                        <ul class="pagination float-right">
                          <%
                            var pageSize = 5;
                            var pRCnt = parseInt(currentPage / pageSize);
                            if(currentPage % pageSize == 0){
                              pRCnt = parseInt(currentPage / pageSize) - 1;
                            }
                            if(currentPage > 5) {
                          %>
                            <li class="page-item">
                              <a class="page-link" data-value="1" aria-label="Previous">
                                <i class="ti-angle-double-left f-12"></i>
                                <span aria-hidden="true"></span>
                                <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                              </a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="page-item">
                              <a class="page-link" data-value=="<%=(pRCnt * pageSize)%>" aria-label="Previous">
                                <i class="ti-angle-left f-12"></i>
                                <span aria-hidden="true"></span>
                                <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                              </a>
                            </li>
                          <% } %>
                          <% for(var index=pRCnt * pageSize + 1;index<(pRCnt + 1)*pageSize + 1;index++){%>
                            <li class= "<%=(currentPage == index) ? 'active' : ''%> page-item">
                              <a class="page-link" data-value="<%=index%>" >
                                <%= index %>
                              </a>
                            </li>
                          <%
                              if(index == pageCount) {
                                break;
                              }
                            }
                          %>
                          <% if((pRCnt + 1) * pageSize < pageCount) { %>
                            <li class="page-item">
                              <a class="page-link" data-value="<%=(pRCnt + 1)*pageSize+1%>" aria-label="Next">
                                <i class="ti-angle-right f-12"></i>
                                <span aria-hidden="true"></span>
                                <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                              </a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="page-item">
                              <a class="page-link" data-value="<%=pageCount%>" aria-label="Next">
                                <i class="ti-angle-double-right f-12"></i>
                                <span aria-hidden="true"></span>
                                <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                              </a>
                            </li>
                          <% } %>
                        </ul>
                      </td>
                      <% } else { %>
                        <td colspan="13">
                          <button id="addBtn" class="btn btn-list alert-check p-r-5 p-l-5 m-l-15 m-b-5  f-left m-t-5"><i class="fas fa-angle-down"></i>선택저장</button>
                        </td>
                      <% } %>
                    </tr>
                  </tfoot>
                </table>
                <input type="hidden" id="page" value="<%=page%>"/>
                <input type="hidden" id="sDate" value="<%=sDate%>"/>
                <input type="hidden" id="eDate" value="<%=eDate%>"/>
                <input type="hidden" id="keyword" value="<%=keyword%>"/>
                <input type="hidden" id="search" value="<%=search%>"/>
                <input type="hidden" id="search2" value="<%=search2%>"/>
                <input type="hidden" id="limit" value="<%=limit%>"/>
                <input type="hidden" id="type" value="<%=type%>"/>
                <input type="hidden" id="site" value="<%=site%>"/>
                <input type="hidden" id="rank" value="<%=rank%>"/>
                <input type="hidden" id="video" value="<%=video%>"/>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
